Oh come, let us sing to Yahweh;\q let us sing joyfully to the rock of our salvation.
\q
2:
Let us enter his presence with thanksgiving;\q let us sing to him with psalms of praise.
\q
3:
For Yahweh is a great God\q and a great King superior to all gods.


\q
4:
In his hand are the depths of the earth;\q the heights of the mountains are his.
\q
5:
The sea is his, for he made it,\q and his hands formed the dry land.


\q

Oh come, let us worship and bow down;\q let us kneel before Yahweh, our creator:
\q

For he is our God,\q and we are the people of his pasture and the sheep of his hand.
